s:0:"";}}s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:121:"http://wpml.org/2013/09/this-week-compatible-cherry-simplicity-gridstack-thinker-sistina-media-grid-wishlist-and-compare/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:130:"http://wpml.org/2013/09/this-week-compatible-cherry-simplicity-gridstack-thinker-sistina-media-grid-wishlist-and-compare/#comments";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"pubDate";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:31:"Sat, 28 Sep 2013 05:45:48 +0000";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:8:"category";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:22:"Compatibility Bulletin";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:4:"guid";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:25:"http://wpml.org/?p=270021";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:11:"isPermaLink";s:5:"false";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:11:"description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:344:"Today we are happy to announce that we have another 5 themes and 3 plugin to add to our compatibility list. The themes are &#8211; Cherry, Simplicity, GridStack, Thinker, Sistina and the plugins are &#8211; Media grid, YITH WooCommerce WishList, YITH WooCommerce Compare. If you want to review the entire Multilingual ready list of themes [...]";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:9:"Dominykas";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:8953:"<p>Today we are happy to announce that we have another 5 themes and 3 plugin to add to our compatibility list. The themes are &#8211; <a href="http://themeforest.net/item/cherry-responsive-ecommerce-theme-for-wp/2765359" target="_blank">Cherry</a>, <a rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img alt="" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/201" />Simplicity</a>, <a href="http://themeforest.net/item/gridstack-responsive-agency-wordpress-theme/5397835" target="_blank">GridStack</a>, <a href="http://themeforest.net/item/thinker-retina-responsive-multipurpose-wp-theme/5562759" target="_blank">Thinker</a>, <a href="http://themeforest.net/item/sistina-flat-multipurpose-shop-theme/5220602" target="_blank">Sistina</a> and the plugins are &#8211; <a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/media-grid-wordpress-responsive-portfolio/2218545" target="_blank">Media grid</a>, <a href="http://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-wishlist/" target="_blank">YITH WooCommerce WishList</a>, <a href="http://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-compare/" target="_blank">YITH WooCommerce Compare</a>.</p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire Multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title="Multilingual Ready Themes " href="http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a title="Multilingual Ready Plugins " href="http://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you&#8217;re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, you are welcome to contact us at <a href="http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/">go global program page</a>. In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a title="Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins" href="http://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a> . It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Cherry theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/cherry-responsive-ecommerce-theme-for-wp/2765359" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-270022" alt="cherry" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/cherry.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Cherry is a responsive theme, suited for e-commerce &amp; business websites. Some features of Cherry are: 10 completely different skins, 5 carousels for featured items, 8 widgets areas and home drag and drop layout.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/cherry-responsive-ecommerce-theme-for-wp/2765359" target="_blank">Purchase Cherry</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Simplicity theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/simplicity-creative-flat-retina-theme/5477244" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-270023" alt="simplicity" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/simplicity.png" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Simplicity theme is a simple, clean and minimalist WordPress theme suitable for business and portfolio. The main features of this theme are: customizable headers, parallax pages, interactive elements, layer slider and smooth scroll.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/simplicity-creative-flat-retina-theme/5477244" target="_blank">Purchase Simplicity</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">GridStack theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/gridstack-responsive-agency-wordpress-theme/5397835" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-270024" alt="gridstack" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/gridstack.png" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>GridStack is unique and modern portfolio theme for agencies, artists and freelancers. With extra wide and parallax-style media, it&#8217;s good for showcasing photos, illustrations, videos and audio.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/gridstack-responsive-agency-wordpress-theme/5397835" target="_blank">Purchase GridStack</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Thinker theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/thinker-retina-responsive-multipurpose-wp-theme/5562759" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-270025" alt="thinker" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/thinker.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Thinker is a responsive and retina ready theme with unlimited skins. This theme is good for businesses, corporations and creative portfolio sites. It has a good number of options and a long list of premium features.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/thinker-retina-responsive-multipurpose-wp-theme/5562759" target="_blank">Purchase Thinker</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Sistina theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/sistina-flat-multipurpose-shop-theme/5220602" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-270026" alt="sistina" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/sistina.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Sistina is a clean and modern Woo Commerce theme, designed with a fresh flat style and with responsive and retina-ready design. The main features of Sistina are: 5 different sliders, header uploaded on each page, 15 custom widgets and 4 portfolio layouts.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/sistina-flat-multipurpose-shop-theme/5220602" target="_blank">Purchase Sistina</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Media grid plugin</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://codecanyon.net/item/media-grid-wordpress-responsive-portfolio/2218545" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-270027" alt="media_grid" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/media_grid.png" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Create responsive and filterable portfolios with ease on your website. Media Grid comes with masonry layout, is designed to adapt each portfolio to any situation and is mobile optimized for responsive themes.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://codecanyon.net/item/media-grid-wordpress-responsive-portfolio/22185452" target="_blank">Purchase Media grid</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">YITH WooCommerce Wishlist plugin</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-wishlist/" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-270029" alt="wishlist" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/09/wishlist.jpg" width="590" height="250" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>With YITH WooCommerce Wishlist you can add a link in each product detail page, in order to add the products to the wishlist page. The plugin will create you the specific page and the products will be added in this page and afterwards add them to the cart or remove them.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://wordpress.org/plugins/yith-woocommerce-wishlist/" target="_blank">Download