3/08/franklin.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Franklin is a wordpress crowdfunding theme, elegant and bloat-free. Franklin gives you the ability to crowdfund your latest project in style. Franklin is designed to work both for single-campaign websites and community oriented crowdfunding websites.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/franklin-wordpress-crowdfunding-theme/5063650" target="_blank">Purchase Franklin</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Stardust theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/stardust-multipurpose-portfolio-wordpress-theme/5254356" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-152478" alt="stardust" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/stardust.png" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Stardust is a multi-purpose portfolio theme. Some features of Stardust are: mix full-width and standard Grid, interactive elements, unlimited colors and sizes for all elements, 500+ Google fonts and a robust backend offers a solution for a variety of business or personal uses.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/stardust-multipurpose-portfolio-wordpress-theme/5254356" target="_blank">Purchase Stardust</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">CuckooBizz theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://creativemarket.com/CuckooThemes/8663-CuckooBizz-One-Page-Parallax-Plus" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-152481" alt="cuckoobizz" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/cuckoobizz.jpg" width="580" height="262" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>CuckooBizz theme can be used for creating a one page site, multiple pages site with one page site homepage functionality or ecommerce site. I