e now compatible with WPML, these are: <a href="http://themeforest.net/item/franklin-wordpress-crowdfunding-theme/5063650" target="_blank">Franklin</a>, <a href="http://themeforest.net/item/stardust-multipurpose-portfolio-wordpress-theme/5254356" target="_blank">Stardust</a>, <a href="https://creativemarket.com/CuckooThemes/8663-CuckooBizz-One-Page-Parallax-Plus" target="_blank">CuckooBizz</a>, <a href="http://colorlabsproject.com/themes/coverage/" target="_blank">Coverage</a>, <a href="http://colorlabsproject.com/themes/arthemia-premium/" target="_blank">Arthemia</a>.</p>\n<p>If you want to review the entire Multilingual ready list of themes and plugins you are welcome to view it here:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a title="Multilingual Ready Themes " href="http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Themes</a></li>\n<li><a title="Multilingual Ready Plugins " href="http://wpml.org/documentation/plugins-compatibility/">Multilingual Ready Plugins</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Also, if you&#8217;re a theme or a plugin author and you want to make it compatible with WPML, you are welcome to contact us at <a href="http://wpml.org/documentation/theme-compatibility/go-global-program/">go global program page</a>. In order to expedite the process we strongly recommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a title="Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins" href="http://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a> . It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Franklin theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/franklin-wordpress-crowdfunding-theme/5063650" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-152495" alt="franklin" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/franklin.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Franklin is a wordpress crowdfunding theme, elegant and bloat-free. Franklin gives you the ability to crowdfund your latest project in style. Franklin is designed to work both for single-campaign websites and community oriented crowdfunding websites.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/franklin-wordpress-crowdfunding-theme/5063650" target="_blank">Purchase Franklin</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Stardust theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/stardust-multipurpose-portfolio-wordpress-theme/5254356" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-152478" alt="stardust" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/stardust.png" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Stardust is a multi-purpose portfolio theme. Some features of Stardust are: mix full-width and standard Grid, interactive elements, unlimited colors and sizes for all elements, 500+ Google fonts and a robust backend offers a solution for a variety of business or personal uses.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/stardust-multipurpose-portfolio-wordpress-theme/5254356" target="_blank">Purchase Stardust</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">CuckooBizz theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://creativemarket.com/CuckooThemes/8663-CuckooBizz-One-Page-Parallax-Plus" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-152481" alt="cuckoobizz" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/cuckoobizz.jpg" width="580" height="262" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>CuckooBizz theme can be used for creating a one page site, multiple pages site with one page site homepage functionality or ecommerce site. Integrated homepage builder allows creating a unique homepage structure, adding content and customizing the appearance of each homepage unit.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="https://creativemarket.com/CuckooThemes/8663-CuckooBizz-One-Page-Parallax-Plus" target="_blank">Purchase CuckooBizz</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Coverage theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://colorlabsproject.com/themes/coverage/" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Coverage-WPML.png" alt="Coverage-WPML" width="590" height="300" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-160310" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Coverage is a solution who has a will to make own blog become a news portal. With a nice design and also attractive features readers can freely discover and choose what news they want to read, all posts you have will be organized on every sections which will made anyone enjoy to read your site.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://colorlabsproject.com/themes/coverage/" target="_blank">Purchase Coverage</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Arthemia theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://colorlabsproject.com/themes/arthemia-premium/" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/Arthemia-WPML.png" alt="Arthemia-WPML" width="590" height="300" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-160308" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Arthemia is a magazine-styled theme. With a good number of numerous built-in features, arthemia will convert your old-fashioned WordPress blog to nice front-end.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://colorlabsproject.com/themes/arthemia-premium/" target="_blank">Purchase Arthemia</a></p>\n</div>\n";s:7:"attri