ecommend that you test your theme or plugin with our <a title="Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins" href="http://wpml.org/documentation/support/achieving-wpml-compatibility-for-your-themes-and-plugins/">Achieving WPML compatibility for your themes and plugins</a> . It easily tests compatibility with WPML and helps you quickly make your theme or plugin <strong>Multilingual Ready</strong>.</p>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Lensa theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://colorlabsproject.com/themes/lensa/" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/Lensa-wpml.png" alt="Lensa-wpml" width="590" height="300" class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-160312" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Lensa is a full-screen WordPress gallery theme designed for those of you who are addicted to high-resolution photography. Lensa functions as an exclusive online photo gallery that looks equally good on desktops, tablets and smartphones.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://colorlabsproject.com/themes/lensa/" target="_blank">Purchase Lensa</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Alfie theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/alfie-the-responsive-bootstrap-wordpress-theme/5017252" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-149172" alt="alfie" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/alfie.jpg" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Alfie is a clean and multi-purpose WordPress theme. It comes with admin panel, packed with various options so you can easily modify stylings, colors, fonts and other aspects of the theme.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/alfie-the-responsive-bootstrap-wordpress-theme/5017252" target="_blank">Purchase Alfie</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Passage theme</h2>\n<p style="text-align: center;"><a href="http://themeforest.net/item/passage-responsive-retina-multipurpose-theme/5188123" rel="attachment wp-att-80782"><img class="aligncenter size-full wp-image-149174" alt="passage" src="http://d2salfytceyqoe.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2013/07/passage1.png" width="590" height="300" /></a></p>\n<blockquote><p>Passage is a multi purpose WordPress theme. Some features of Passage are: 4 fluid AJAX animated transitions between pages for a creative experience, standard small/normal/large grid for header, counters and horizontal graphs.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://themeforest.net/item/passage-responsive-retina-multipurpose-theme/5188123" target="_blank">Purchase Passage</a></p>\n</div>\n<div class="feature">\n<h2 style="text-align: center;">Search In Place plugin</h2>\n<blockquote><p>Search in Place improves blog search by displaying query results in real time. It displays the results dynamically as you enter the search criteria.</p></blockquote>\n<p><a class="button download-button vt-p" href="http://wordpress.org/plugins/search-in-place/" target="_blank">Download Search In Place</a></p>\n</div>\n";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:91:"http://wpml.org/2013/07/now-compatible-lensa-alfie-passage-and-search-in-place-plugin/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"0";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}}}}}s:27:"http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom";a:1:{s:4:"link";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:3:{s:4:"href";s:21:"http: